(146, 1, 'Thu, 28 Jun 2018 16:52:04 -0400', 'Amazon takes on pharmacy sector with new acquisition', '<p><a href="https://www.yahoo.com/news/amazon-moves-disrupt-pharmacy-sector-acquisition-151655365.html"><img src="http://l1.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/s4K4p2BZZGk8ij9XG21vzA--/YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b247aD04Njt3PTEzMDs-/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/afp.com/2094fa5c36d7c31f2b47ed6ffc6ac6a0d4d45170.jpg" width="130" height="86" alt="Amazon takes on pharmacy sector with new acquisition" align="left" title="Amazon takes on pharmacy sector with new acquisition" border="0" ></a>Amazon set its sights on the pharmacy market Thursday with the acquisition of tech-focused retailer PillPack, sending shock waves through the sector over prospects of disruption by the US online colossus.  Amazon has long been rumored to be interested in the pharmacy business, and the entry by a powerful new player could unsettle a business dominated by large American chains including CVS and Walgreens.  Terms were not disclosed on the deal for PillPack, an online pharmacy which operates in all 50 US states and offers pre-sorted dose packaging and home delivery.<p><br clear="all">', 'https://www.yahoo.com/news/amazon-moves-disrupt-pharmacy-sector-acquisition-151655365.html', '2018-06-29 23:51:33', '', 'news'),
(147, 1, 'Thu, 28 Jun 2018 00:31:01 -0400', 'Frustration, heartbreak for migrant parents looking for kids', '<p><a href="https://www.yahoo.com/news/justice-spokesman-urges-congress-action-divided-families-124027046.html"><img src="http://l2.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/99dloHghJ7.IyNZEKvX9Lg--/YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b247aD04Njt3PTEzMDs-/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/ap_webfeeds/53c69cf90ed745399e01ed4908f91d59.jpg" width="130" height="86" alt="Frustration, heartbreak for migrant parents looking for kids" align="left" title="Frustration, heartbreak for migrant parents looking for kids" border="0" ></a>EL PASO, Texas (AP) â€” In an unmarked brick building a few blocks from the Mexican border, immigrant parents clutched folders of birth certificates and asylum paperwork and sat on folding chairs, waiting to use a single, shared landline phone.<p><br clear="all">', 'https://www.yahoo.com/news/justice-spokesman-urges-congress-action-divided-families-124027046.html', '2018-06-29 23:51:33', '', 'news'),
(148, 1, 'Fri, 29 Jun 2018 04:08:11 -0400', 'Bali airport reopens as volcano rumbles', '<p><a href="https://www.yahoo.com/news/indonesia-shuts-bali-airport-friday-due-ash-volcano-000007857.html"><img src="http://l1.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/KfmViO6sTc46.tPw0I7J.w--/YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b247aD04Njt3PTEzMDs-/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/Reuters/2018-06-29T213210Z_1_LYNXMPEE5S29O_RTROPTP_2_INDONESIA-VOLCANO.JPG" width="130" height="86" alt="Bali airport reopens as volcano rumbles" align="left" title="Bali airport reopens as volcano rumbles" border="0" ></a>By Sultan Ashori  DENPASAR, Indonesia (Reuters) - The airport on Indonesia''s holiday island of Bali reopened on Friday after ash from a volcano forced a brief closure and the cancellation of more than 300 flights.  Mount Agung in northeastern Bali has been rumbling to life intermittently since late last year and it began belching smoke and ash again on Thursday.  It was shooting a column of ash more than 2,500 meters (8,200 feet) into the sky on Friday and officials said operations at Indonesia''s second-busiest airport would be reviewed every few hours.<p><br clear="all">', 'https://www.yahoo.com/news/indonesia-shuts-bali-airport-friday-due-ash-volcano-000007857.html', '2018-06-29 23:51:33', '', 'news'),
